# ======================================================================
# STM32CubeMX Project Configuration file
# Project: f411-motor-cube
# MCU: STM32F411CEUx (Black Pill F411CE)
# Toolchain / IDE: STM32CubeIDE / PlatformIO (framework=stm32cube)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# This file is the source of truth for CubeMX-driven peripheral
# configuration. Open it in STM32CubeMX to edit / regenerate code.
#
# ISSUE-D cleanup: removed TIM6 (F411 has no TIM6/TIM7 basic timers),
# removed invalid F411 RCC fields (Ethernet, LCDTFT, PLLSAI2/3,
# HCLK3/4, RGMIIClk, QSPI, SAI, SPDIFRX, SDIO, USB, VCO3),
# removed TIM6_DAC_IRQn from NVIC.
# ======================================================================

